===Noun===
'''céntimo'''
# A monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Costa Rican]] [[colón]].
# A monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Peruvian]] [[nuevo sol]].
# A monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Philippine]] [[peso]].
# A monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Bolivian]] [[peseta]].
# A former monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Spanish]] [[peseta]].
# A former monetary [[subdivision]], equivalent to a 1/100th of a [[Mozambican]] [[metica]].

